Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:47.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\fs60\bord7.5\3c&H0100EF&\pos(960,1072.5)}吸一口气用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:52.13,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\fs60\bord7.5\3c&H0100EF&\pos(960,1072.5)}屏住呼吸悄悄走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.55,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\fs60\bord7.5\3c&H0100EF&\pos(960,1072.5)}又是和平的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\fs60\bord7.5\3c&H0100EF&\pos(960,1072.5)}谢谢大家的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}富国强兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们太超过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫尾须美之章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园子的梦 其三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作为对你们给学弟妹洗脑的处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}禁止你们吃乌冬面一周
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这…这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}吃不到乌冬面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不好了 得赶快去医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.03,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫尾须美之章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过须美 别把家里阿姨的工作都抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感觉不做点什么就静不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难得星期天 和乃木她们去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}银有事 所以我们就自由行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那须美 你也随心一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想银办完事后 会找我出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园园也可能跟之前一样 突然来家里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你交到好朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H206236&\frx344\fry356\frz17.6\pos(384,516)}在站前跟家人买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H206236&\frx344\fry356\pos(462,693)\frz17.6}我也在那里逛街呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.32,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H206236&\frx344\fry356\frz13.18\pos(366,684)}园园迷路了的话\N\N\N\N\h就打几次名字吧\N\N\N\N\h\h辛苦银了
