Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:32.47,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H434824&\frz12.62\frx344\fry348\pos(633,1017)}我是乃木园子
