Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H434824&\frx344\fry348\frz15.97\pos(711,927)}我是乃木园子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已经迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}结果我们三个还是聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者天生会互相吸引嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还好银找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们要不要跟你家人打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不用啦 你也认识我爸妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且我不习惯这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}全家放假一起出门购物 好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}遇到认识的就不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在也没事了 我接下来跟你们一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}先稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好啦 我的好弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别因为姐姐这么有人气就难受呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}笑一个笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}休息的日子要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}又要恢复警戒态势了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}得打起精神来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然新生教育有点羞耻…不过好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}时间过得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只有我跟你们不同路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}须美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不会 我懂你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你是觉得假期要结束了 有点不舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然我说自己擅长休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过想想肩负的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感觉也不敢彻底地放松下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要我们在一起 这份担心就是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫也这么觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}脸上都这么写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是Vertex破坏了神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这些快乐的日子也会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定要阻止这种情况 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我当然也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但一直这样我就回不了家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}解散解散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想到了 开一次合宿会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不错 就选在银家里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我家吗 我家有两个弟弟呢
Comment: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:59.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}何を忘れてきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:05.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}廊下急いで戻る教室
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:11.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}窓をスクリーンにして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:17.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}茜色した日々の名残り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:23.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一人の力じゃ小さくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:31.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}だから勇気持ち寄った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}君の声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:44.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}君の光が奏でるかけがえのないこの時を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}君の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:56.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}君のぬくもりと一緒に閉じ込めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:02.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一つになどなれなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:07.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}重ね合わせていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:59.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}感觉忘记了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:05.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}穿过走廊急匆匆跑回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:11.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}倒映在窗玻璃上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:17.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}是染成夕阳色的日常点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:23.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一个人双拳难敌四手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:31.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}所以大家把勇气凑在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:44.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}你的光芒演奏了这段独一无二的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:56.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}你的温存我都会悉心收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:02.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}纵使不能合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:07.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}也让我们肩并着肩一同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者就看气势和骨气！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:17.41,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎 两只？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是怎样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:18.83,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}它将我的箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真开心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:20.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不愧是园园
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}滚出 我们的家园！
